infoparam.name: UML Note
infoparam.value:
• The electrically-assisted bicycle needs to be recharged when decelerating to avoid any autonomy problem.
• The bike needs to have a max speed of 25 km/h.
• The pedal assistance needs to be an availible option • ----- The console needs to give you the option to choose the level of assistance • ----- Levels of assistances needs to be ranging from 0% to 100% (going through 25% and 50%)
• The batery needs to be recharging on deceleration. • The batery needs to be recharging on the mains. • The batery needs to be recharging when pedaling backwards. • Autonomy needs to be 100Km using the deceleration cherging feature.
• The electrically-assisted bicycle needs to be able be connected to your smart device (Android or IOS). • The motor of the bike needs to have an anti thaft security • ----- The anti-theft security needs to be able to be activated from the connected device
• The electrically-assisted bicycle console needs to be located on the handlebars. • The console needs to display how much battery power is left.

• The console needs to display how much battery power is left.
